n有咩事上黎傾 大把人開解你<br />\n<br />\n老實講, 屋企人唔支持好正常 唔需要傷心<br />\n佢地已經係收成期 根本唔會理其他人<br />\n<br />\n所謂既血唔血緣關係 都係呃鳩人 唔好被呢D既無謂又戇鳩既野捆綁住<br />\n係呢度個個都係巴打絲打"},{"pid":"76c2c6f04e9b54c1a1d91d2fb550199593406428","tid":1606781,"uid":40054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T13:23:47.000Z","msg":"情緒病有可以係基因家族遺傳 你媽媽有 有機會你都有 暫時唔好太關注啲負面野先 分散下注意力 做下自己中意做既野 搵人吹下水 唔想你有事 巴打 take care"},{"pid":"c5e311401800e285c3b9508c886a4d533d6f588f","tid":1606781,"uid":178066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T13:26:08.000Z","msg":"會唔會想搬出去？<br />\n有咩要幫手即管出聲啊巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b64c8ef761a81d6726c6ed95236c76d98fc7cb1","tid":1606781,"uid":324701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T13:28:39.000Z","msg":"唔好呀～做下文宣派下傳單就算囉，唔好睇唔開呀<br />\n你媽媽可能都係擔心你先精神病發，暫時唔出住可能會好轉呢"},{"pid":"8c4b3d65863cd1ef60c56e474439c8610640c786","tid":1606781,"uid":321906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T13:29:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"06aee82cf1481f5d6d206d01c2ca26187ce94e3d","tid":1606781,"uid":243385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:21:39.000Z","msg":"照顧好自己唔成為其他人既負累先係對自己負責任既行為"},{"pid":"6158d0e84a0f337c01c331d8452db2854fa7ab36","tid":1606781,"uid":67315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8191297f77eb873beb84c7a764403dc12d8d429","tid":1606781,"uid":198607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7db10796058066f1c52fe03d863b66f4f3051f9e","tid":1606781,"uid":67315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T12:40:44.000Z","msg":"樓主？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T12:59:29.000Z","msg":"仲係到 放心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:28:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce6d94b0b4bb8df07982f5e997d80d0482329fdd","tid":1606781,"uid":122139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"033ff02e2a5ae473aeafae44f37ece85d3