e":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fde7f3088d27a27baa654c4b6c194c7ccb97f004","tid":1606781,"uid":63759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:19:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:40:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ebcaa44b008f036e4fe3d7e977d2ac224f3a9bb","tid":1606781,"uid":271706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:41:30.000Z","msg":"陪下屋企人先<br />\n你自己都休息下<br />\n因為以後仲有好長嘅路要行"},{"pid":"073bf396f5b9d8b60990625b3134a3488722764f","tid":1606781,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:47:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c423cc96718db3fb87d3578d18ec7409e2b0198","tid":1606781,"uid":118945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T22:22:46.000Z","msg":"我喺度 <br />\n手足一個都不能少<br />\n乖"},{"pid":"522c9fa12d2f2bc567a3774d76c830e9b2cc9690","tid":1606781,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T22:51:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"282c24758cd95820303cacd3305a5ae5f2a18a17","tid":1606781,"uid":21783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T22:57:02.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好，一個都不能少"},{"pid":"a0a5ae2ddc46e6c6402fd02f4808e536b542e461","tid":1606781,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"033ff02e2a5ae473aeafae44f37ece85d356bce4","tid":1606781,"uid":198607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:56:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T09:12:44.000Z","msg":"或許我不能完全了解你內心的痛苦，但我明白置身痛苦中是怎樣一回事，因為我也是身在香港的一份子。無論你的是否想放棄自己，也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡，因鬱結和壓力積存太多，到情緒爆發時可能已超出你的控制。你不如停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6kYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=5f638e7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關<br />\n難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"3ace16ee539a9c84233511945334f17ed72da7fe","tid":1606781,"uid":221093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:54:30.000Z","msg":"樓主你呢個星期點呀?"},{"pid":"f4bee1a9f8cace707615b81fb2e33089398a8b7d","tid":1606781,"uid":198607,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3ace16ee539a9c84233511945334f17ed72da7fe","tid":1606781,"uid":221093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:54:30.000Z","msg":"樓主你呢個星期點呀?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T01:23:16.000Z","msg":"比起之前好咗 多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁關心"},{"pid":"547859f94f58059b3706bf1346149ac85df0b63a","tid":1606781,"uid":212436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T01:58:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"826e96c7a891ccff4e98afc9979db813c00171e9","tid":1606781,"uid":221093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4bee1a9f8cace707615b81fb2e33089398a8b7d","tid":1606781,"uid":198607,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3ace16ee539a9c84233511945334f17ed72da7fe","tid":1606781,"uid":221093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:54:30.000Z","msg":"樓主你呢個星期點呀?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T01:23:16.000Z","msg":"比起之前好咗 多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.